## Prerequisites

- Linux
- Python 3.7+
- PyTorch 1.8+
- CUDA 10.1+
- [MMCV](https://mmcv.readthedocs.io/en/latest/#installation)
- [MMDetection](https://mmdetection.readthedocs.io/en/latest/#installation)

